#!/usr/bin/env ssc
---
name: spinner-test
description: Unit tests for the Spinner component — run with `ssc test`.
---

# Spinner tests

[Spinner](./spinner.ssc)

```scalascript
test("default render is non-empty", () => Spinner.render("md").nonEmpty)
test("sm render contains size class", () => Spinner.render("sm").contains("sm"))
test("lg render contains size class", () => Spinner.render("lg").contains("lg"))
test("render has role=status", () => Spinner.render("md").contains("role=\"status\""))
test("css is non-empty", () => Spinner.css.nonEmpty)
test("css contains animation", () => Spinner.css.contains("animation"))
```
